comments: Jokic (DEN) establishes a legal position in Dellavedova's (CLE) path and slightly extends his arms as they disengage from the pick.
Dellavedova (CLE) establishes a legal guarding position outside the RA before the pass is released and absorbs the contact initiated by Millsap (DEN).
Barton (DEN) makes marginal body contact with Dellavedova (CLE) as he dribbles the ball into the front court.
Love (CLE) initiates marginal contact with Barton (DEN) as he pivots to face the basket during his post move.

Osman (CLE) extends his arm into Bartons (DEN) back at the end of the drive, affecting the contact between Barton and Love (CLE), who had established a legal guarding position outside the RA before the pass was released and contact occurred.
Harris (DEN) makes contact to the arm of Osman (CLE) that affects his SQBR.
Osman (CLE) slightly extends his arm into Millsap (DEN) at the end of his drive however the contact initiated is marginal.
Harris (DEN) maintains a bent forearm to Love's (CLE) side and does not extend or apply force as Love (CLE) extends towards the basket during his driving shot attempt.
Jokic (DEN) makes contact with Love's (CLE) hand on ball during the rebound.
Nance Jr. (CLE) makes marginal contact to Barton's (DEN) hand at the end of the drive however, Barton (DEN) is able to move through the contact to make his desired pass.

Milsap (DEN) initially gets his hand on the ball and disrupts Thompsons (CLE) upward motion. Thompson regains control and has started his upward motion toward the rim when Jokic (DEN) makes contact with his arm.
Jokic (DEN) establishes himself in a legal screening position in the path of Dellavedova (CLE) and absorbs the contact.
